_pdbx_database_remark.text   
;SHEET
THE SHEET PRESENTED AS *S9* ON SHEET RECORDS BELOW IS
ACTUALLY A SEVEN-STRANDED BETA-BARREL.  THIS IS REPRESENTED
BY AN EIGHT-STRANDED SHEET IN WHICH THE FIRST AND LAST
STRANDS ARE IDENTICAL.
DOMAIN 3 (RESIDUES 553 - 639) HAS A VERY COMPLICATED
HYDROGEN BONDING NETWORK WHICH IS DIFFICULT TO DESCRIBE.
IN THE SHEET RECORDS BELOW, THIS IS SIMPLIFIED BY REGARDING
SEVERAL PAIRS OF BETA-STRANDS AS ONE.
;
# 
